don’t hold back.

186
00:10:06,173 --> 00:10:09,443
Razor: Heh. Fine. Does that mean
that I can kill him?

187
00:10:09,476 --> 00:10:14,047
Ging: Don’t underestimate him.
He is my kid.

188
00:10:15,449 --> 00:10:18,018
I’m counting on you.
Thanks, razor.

189
00:10:19,486 --> 00:10:22,389
Razor: I always thought
your dad was a little bit crazy.

190
