200
00:10:45,579 --> 00:10:47,214
Ging: I’m counting on you.

201
00:10:47,247 --> 00:10:48,315
Thanks, razor.

202
00:10:48,348 --> 00:10:50,183
♪

203
00:10:54,421 --> 00:10:56,890
