of everybody else.

211
00:11:17,110 --> 00:11:19,212
Razor: That was great teamwork.

212
00:11:19,246 --> 00:11:20,247
Gon: Yeah!

213
00:11:21,348 --> 00:11:25,118
Razor: Now go find ging.

214
00:11:27,054 --> 00:11:28,122
Gon: Okay!

215
