a life of their own.

233
00:12:24,011 --> 00:12:28,983
But razor and his pirate friends
simply wouldn’t believe us.

234
00:12:29,016 --> 00:12:30,985
Gon: Oh.

235
00:12:31,018 --> 00:12:34,255
Woman: Those who live
off the bounty of the sea

236
00:12:34,288 --> 00:12:36,590
can never defile it.

237
00:12:37,624 --> 00:12:39,359
Or that’s what they said

238
00:12:39,393 --> 00:12:42,196
