with their secrets.

239
00:12:42,229 --> 00:12:45,432
Killua: Hey, don’t forget, okay?

240
00:12:45,465 --> 00:12:47,600
It’s just a story
in a video game.

241
00:12:48,635 --> 00:12:50,470
